","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" The problem is humans. You're all selfish, rotten liars.\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Boss:"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" What kind of team-building exercise will fix that? "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Dogbert:"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" I'd try\nsomething involving DNA and alien technology."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"}],"tagName":"blockquote","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"It is one of my fundamental learning as an agile consultant and practitioner:\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Humans are Liars"}],"tagName":"strong","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":". They lie about their feelings, performance, thoughts,\ncoworkers, progress, ..., in order to protect themselves. And this is the root\ncause for all organizational problems. Humans are really great in adapting to\nexisting organizational deficits and turning them to something which they can\noperate in with the least amount of energy necessary."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"In order to break this pattern and create a workplace that enables humans to\nfocus on their positive skills (creativity, problem solving, ‚Ä¶) these three\nfactors are key in a workplace culture:"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"It should be safe to be vulnerable"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{